{"tid":2302832,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"( 社評 ) 任何明顯 挑釁/挑撥/分化/無聊 topic 既 post 唔使覆, 唔使理，由佢沉, 正負評都唔須要。","createTime":"2020-11-27T12:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T00:40:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8b49561c360b2d26fae78726363e1e741e1a91","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T12:10:36.000Z","msg":"( 社評 ) 任何明顯 挑釁/挑撥/分化/無聊 topic 既 post 唔使覆, 唔使理，由佢沉, 正負評都唔須要。<br />\n<br />\n無謂變相幫助推呢類 post 洗版。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">真係忍唔到要覆既, 就用不推文回覆</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">無謂畀個標題浮面。</span><br />\n<br />\n----------------<br />\n<br />\n收到！ 標題同內文都會review<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">其實最好都係唔好覆， 由佢沉。</span><br />\n<br />\n因為就算你用 不推文回覆 覆咗個 post,<br />\n佢就有機會用 推文回覆 咋啼駁你，<br />\n咁個 post 又有機會浮返面。"},{"pid":"c0d0f720262a792453ce39175d5e7b8c0e379077","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2302829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2302829</a>"},{"pid":"95008ccc94eada876ab9c9e3d99baf24efeeeb1e","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先識善用不推文回覆嚟屌三毛/ATTENTION WHORE?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2303702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2303702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"197140f7a94639748a0f2548cf6e0e893ec123e2","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95008ccc94eada876ab9c9e3d99baf24efeeeb1e","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先識善用不推文回覆嚟屌三毛/ATTENTION WHORE?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2303702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/230370