容。佢地真係同路人？大家試諗下，如果真係手足係會俾建議幫手補鑊，即使有唔同意見亦唔會淨係留言不斷笑香港人送頭嘅撚樣，冷嘲熱諷撚一黎只會對件事無幫助，二黎只會散播失敗風同打擊士氣，令人遺憾嘅有唔少傻仔上咗呢一班人嘅當連自己都講埋一份。呢一班究竟係咩人，自己諗。"},{"pid":"70fe642f045aabe48d4b2ebbd5c00dd5e0d7c72d","tid":2302832,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">發現疑似五毛，字裏行間不斷浮現出踩港思維</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wbsvNxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbsvNxZ.png&h=8383b832&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhFk9Mk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhFk9Mk.png&h=de9a2e08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfb7cb993bb5f5a33e8db9bfe6c57f08c09a2e8e","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T17:08:10.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2302829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2302829</a>"},{"pid":"52319b56fa55fb3da57a972e1beb3f5201468739","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1906447b9aa30e8a69d14bc5f40b0c840b0e3b71","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2302829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2302829</a>"},{"pid":"09d88b8f85c8a719fb39c68e0db5e834867ad178","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2302829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2302829</a>"},{"pid":"72f8f307